Q10
Consider the following method.

        public static int mystery(int[] arr) {
            int sum = 0;
            for (int i = 0; i < arr.length - 1; i++) {
                sum += arr[i] * arr[i + 1];
            }
            return sum;
        }

What is mystery({1, 2, 3, 4})?

